# Noetfield self-audit loop (mandatory)

Follow [docs/ops/AGENT_SELF_AUDIT_LOOP_LOCKED_v1.md](../../docs/ops/AGENT_SELF_AUDIT_LOOP_LOCKED_v1.md).

## Session start

1. Read [.cursor/agent-memory/MEMORY_LOCKED.yaml](../agent-memory/MEMORY_LOCKED.yaml) — includes **R-011**
2. Read [.cursor/incidents/REGISTRY.md](../incidents/REGISTRY.md) open items
3. Apply [.cursor/skills/SKILL-001-scope-gate-before-work.md](../skills/SKILL-001-scope-gate-before-work.md)
4. Apply [.cursor/skills/SKILL-008-agentic-commercial-boundary.md](../skills/SKILL-008-agentic-commercial-boundary.md)
5. Read [FOUNDER_AGENTIC_COMMERCIAL_AND_NO_CURSOR_AUTORUN_LOCKED_v1.md](../../docs/ops/FOUNDER_AGENTIC_COMMERCIAL_AND_NO_CURSOR_AUTORUN_LOCKED_v1.md)

## Before commit

- [.cursor/skills/SKILL-002-pre-commit-audit.md](../skills/SKILL-002-pre-commit-audit.md)
- `./scripts/verify-agent-scope.sh` must pass

## Docs

- Tag + date **only on docs you write** — never retag or edit others' docs ([AGENT_DOC_TAGGING_LOCKED_v1.md](../../docs/ops/AGENT_DOC_TAGGING_LOCKED_v1.md))

